						<summary>

						<p>On a stone near Bathina Musalayya's house.</p>						

						<p>Dated Śaka 1141, <hi rend="italic">Māgha,</hi> ba. 2, Thursday (1223 A.D., January 19).</p>						

						<p>Registers the gift of 55 goats for a perpetual lamp in the temple of Amarēśvara of Dannāḍa by Māra-boya, son of Chandana-boya.</p>						

