<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī śubha sa 
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ṁvatsaraṁbulu 1141 
<lb n="3"/>ṁḍagu mā<unclear>gha</unclear> bahala(huḷa) 
<lb n="4"/>vidiyayu guruvārā 
<lb n="5" break="no"/>na caṁpa(da)nabōI(yi)ni koḍku 
